snippet.title: Five Dates - An Interactive Rom-Com (Official Trailer)
snippet.description:
Five Dates is an interactive rom-com about the unpredictable world of digital dating. With five potential female matches, Vinny explores whether compatibility, chemistry and connection is still possible in a world where physical touch is no longer an option.

Coming to App Store on February 14
Pre-order now on App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/five-dates/id1549664599

Out now on PC & Mac (Steam), PS4, Xbox One and Nintendo Switch.

Steam: https://bit.ly/5datespc
Xbox One: https://bit.ly/5datesxo
PS4: https://bit.ly/5datesps 
Switch: https://bit.ly/5datesns

Developed by Good Gate Media and Wales Interactive. 
Published by Wales Interactive. 

Cast
Taheen Modak (Two Weeks To Live)
Mandip Gill (Doctor Who, Suspicion, The Flood)
Demmy Ladipo (The Last Tree, Enterprice)
Georgia Hirst (Vikings, Ravers)
Georgia Small, Marisa Abela (Lena Dunham’s Industry, Cobra)
Sinéad Harnett (UK singer/influencer)

Follow Wales Interactive:

Twitter: https://twitter.com/WalesInter
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/WalesInteractive
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/walesinteractive
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/publisher/WalesInteractive
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/walesinteractive
